	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Valde et supra modum doleo casum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglicanę</placeName> ecclesię, mi frater in domino venerande; cuperem centies mori quam de nostris ecclesiis tale quidpiam experiri.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Extendit dominus iratam manum suam in nos multoties commeritos, ut, nisi dominus suos ad se rapuerit, vereor lamentabiliora experturos esse; tam induruit cor nostrum in malitia et immensa ingratitudine erga oblatum nobis dei inenarrabile beneficium.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">O domine, libera tuos e tam perverso sęculo, ne patiare nomen tuum diutius blasphemari.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Spero brevi nos abituros, mi frater, in eternam patriam; faxit deus, ut, quod reliquum nobis est vitę, pro ipsius veritate et gloria multa animi parrhesia impendamus.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Alias mediocriter valeo cum uxore et liberis.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Filia <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p6505" cert="high">Anna</persName> nondum michi reconciliata est; forte eius nulla tangitur cura.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Man sagt mir gloubwirdig, myn gegenschwäher der pfarrer zuͦ <placeName type="auto_name">Gauchlingen</placeName> halte sich gar übel und uneerlich; er hure alßo, das imme aber, wie vormals ouch beschähen, ein uneelich kind werde.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name">Constantinus der jung</persName> trybt unmäßliche hochfart und muͤtwyll; ich sorg übel, myn tochter syge ubel verfaren.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Der herr wolle es mitt sinen gnaden beßeren.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus tecum.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale cum omnibus tuis, uxore et liberis.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutat te arcis et urbis praefectus et precipue <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8369" cert="high">Hammanus</persName> noster.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Datum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l285" cert="high">Lentzburgi</placeName> 10. septembris 1553.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p8440" cert="high">Gervasius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fideli Christi servo <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, domino fratri et veteri amico charissimo, ad manus.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
